==Useful Info==
'''Frost giants''' are enormous frozen humanoids who wield [[freezing]] [[battleaxe]]s and chill everything in their path with icy bolts. They have [[cold resistance]] and feel at home in cold-themed [[branch]]es such as the [[Ice Cave]], as well as [[the Vaults]], [[the Depths]], and the lower levels of [[the Dungeon]].

{{monster spells}}

==Tips & Tricks==
*[[Cold]] resistance is obviously helpful against them, but be aware that their physical melee damage is still very significant.
*They have a tendency to carry +2 battleaxes of freezing. They rarely carry +0 triple swords of freezing.
